{"word":"G4345 - προσκληρόω - prosklēróō - pros-klay-ro'-o - Consort with","slug":"G4345","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσκληρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prosklēróō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pros-klay-ro'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Consort with"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - proskle&#x0304;roo&#x0304;</b> - <i>pros-klay-ro'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G2820\">G2820</a>; to <i>give</i> a common <i>lot to</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>associate with:</i> - consort with."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2624\">G2624</a>, <a href=\"#/G2816\">G2816</a>, <a href=\"#/G2817\">G2817</a>, <a href=\"#/G2818\">G2818</a>, <a href=\"#/G2819\">G2819</a>, <a href=\"#/G2820\">G2820</a>, <a href=\"#/G3647\">G3647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3648\">G3648</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789\">G4789</a>"}]}